nodes.text: Darth Vader and the Lost Command 5
Darth Vader and the Lost Command 5 is the last issue of the Star Wars: Darth Vader and the Lost Command comic mini-series written by W. Haden Blackman.
The final battle with the insurgents brings a resolution to the mystery of Moff Tarkin's son.
Vader resolves the entire mission in a way that only he, the darkest lord of the Sith, can!
